 reasons (it is somewhere between hard and impossible for shareholders of m=
ost public companies to call special meetings, if it happens lots of invest=
ors will show up, shareholders vote on the board and not the CEO directly, =
the CEO can=E2=80=99t just wire herself the company=E2=80=99s money, etc.),=
 but it is funny to imagine.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also if the company exists in a video game I g=
